Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:17.47,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\bord0.5\c&HDFECF9&\1a&H3C&\pos(45,45)\p1}m -20 -20 l 375 -20 375 320 -20 320
